<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和观音菩萨飞过了大海，回到了那条宽阔的大河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨在空中叫道：“妖龙！立刻从河里出来。唐僧来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那条龙从河里出来行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨。”他说，“对不起。我不知道唐僧已经来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我正要休息时，有只讨厌的猴子... ...”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当那条龙看到观音菩萨旁边的悟空时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他愣了一下：“就是那只猴子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是孙悟空。”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他陪唐僧前去取经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那猴子没告诉我啊！”龙说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我问过他是谁，但他没回答我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”观音菩萨说。她看了悟空一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从现在开始，你必须告诉别人你是谁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一路上还会有其他人等着你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨又看了看那条龙：“你要驮着唐僧去西天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那条龙全身开始发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当光慢慢变暗后，那条龙不见了，原地出现了一匹马。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它看上去和唐僧原先的那匹马一模一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨离开后，悟空把马牵到了唐僧面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你把马找回来了。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是的。”悟空说，“观音菩萨来过这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把那条龙变成了马。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他本来就是要与我们一起去取经的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧跪在地上向天敬拜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“站起来吧，师父。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨现在已经回到普陀山了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要渡河吗？”一个声音叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了看四周。一条船靠到了岸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会带你们渡河的。”船夫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧踏上了船，悟空牵着马也跟着上了船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船夫划船过了河，一路上一句话都没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了河的另一边，悟空牵着马上了岸。唐僧下了船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他转身准备去感谢船夫时，那条船已经不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看到唐僧困惑的表情时笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是那条河的河神。”悟空解释说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧和悟空继续翻山越岭，走过一个个平原。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去西天要多长时间啊？”有一天下午唐僧问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很久很久。”悟空说，“我们几乎是刚开始我们的旅程。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们又走了一段时间，来到了一座寺院前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们就在这里过夜吧。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是僧人。寺院的和尚会很乐意提供给我们食物和睡觉的地方的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天夜里，师徒二人与庙里的和尚一起吃饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当住持听到唐僧从哪里来时，他非常激动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们会取到真经的。”住持说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那真的是最高的荣誉。观音菩萨怎么选中你的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她说只有真正的信徒才能取到真经。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我试穿过一件袈裟，然后她看出来我是真正的信徒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你带了那件袈裟吗？”住持问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“带了啊！”唐僧说，“那是佛祖的宝贝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸手从包里拿出了那件袈裟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>住持的眼睛亮了：“能让我看看吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧把袈裟递给了住持。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>住持赞叹地看着袈裟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我今晚能借用一下这件袈裟吗？就今晚！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧犹豫了一会儿：“可以。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天深夜，住持没有睡觉，一直盯着袈裟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能把这件袈裟还回去。这是属于我的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>